version_description:
Updates to the Starbucks UK app

We have taken your feedback on board and have released an updated version of the Starbucks UK app. You can now track:

- Your current Star balance more easily
- Progress towards your next Reward
- Stars until you reach Gold status

We have also made some bug fixes and improvements.

We will continue to make improvements based on your feedback so look out for more updates to come.

Note: The new currently app doesn’t support Apple Watch, please accept our apologies for any inconvenience this may cause.

Added additional Realm issues logging
Improvements on Realm

We have made it easier to:
• Manage your cards
• Place orders
• View store information

We’ve also included some essential performance improvements.
